{"tid":586536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉蔚琳復工出車　獲乘客鼓勵　支持車長工業行動","createTime":"2018-03-09T15:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T15:10:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b79413afa1e00db4cd9d036789b46d8d4d7c3717","tid":586536,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"九巴早前解僱「月薪車長大聯盟」葉蔚琳等人引起眾怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隨後決定暫緩解僱決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。葉蔚琳及丈夫劉卓恒今日終於正式出車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，獲安排駕駛234X路線的巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。有乘客發現司機是葉蔚琳後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，表示支持他們的工業行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%91%89%E8%94%9A%E7%90%B3%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8A-%E7%8D%B2%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%259A%25E7%2590%25B3%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&d=RCy%2F34UwP%2Bv8XPXFD%2BhNpgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=7f1ef551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%259A%25E7%2590%25B3%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5-%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&h=5b2ed4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E8%91%89%E8%94%9A%E7%90%B3%E5%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%87%BA%E8%BB%8A-%E7%8D%B2%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/</a>"},{"pid":"9bfd4cc92372ca125cf8ef49e014e2ab6efb2085","tid":586536,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"葉蔚琳的巴士在晚上七時許於尖東開出。她聲線沙啞地向記者透露，之前罷工時連撐兩日沒睡，這幾天休息還好，身體雖然感到累但仍然支撐到，「人最緊要開心，頂到經歷下，人無幾多次這樣機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yip2_cnTmq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyip2_cnTmq_1200x0.png&h=8d3eb852&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n她表示，今日與丈夫在車廠內坐了一會，公司就叫她出特別班車，但塞了個多小時才到尖東麼地道的總站。她在紅燈停車時對記者說，在路上沒辦法說話，因為開車就是要開車，不可以因自己的事影響到班車。"},{"pid":"a8915d4f3346f34fe6ee16b9b7503306c3d1dd57","tid":586536,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"有車上乘客表示，支持車長工業行動。其中宋小姐及伍小姐都是住在深水埗，平日每天搭九巴，今日上課後回家乘此特別班車，想不到就遇上了葉車長。宋小姐覺得車長爭取權益沒什麼不妥，影響也不大，公司不應一來就秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kmb_UBzjl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkmb_UBzjl_1200x0.png&h=aed7f142&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n平日他們對九巴車長服務印象已很好，有75分，舉例指曾見過有車長遷就有需要傷殘人士，會主動把車駕近路邊讓輪椅下車。<br />\n<br />\n「一定是公司未能改善待遇，他們才會要走到這一步。」伍小姐說。<br />\n<br />\n他們支持工業行動，「沒問題！沒理由樣樣say yes吧？」 伍亦認為九巴反應太極端、無人性！<br />\n<br />\n宋小姐則批評，九巴未有作出警告就解僱員工，「我覺得是殺雞儆猴，敢出來說就先打低你」，認為九巴高層應酌情處理。她又指大埔車禍令他們了解到車長工作壓力很大，有時乘客也會辱罵他們，而兼職的也需要更多訓練。<br />\n<br />\n「香港肯出來說公道說話的很少。」宋小姐說。「如忍讓也不能改變到的話，是不是有需要出來發聲呢？」"},{"pid":"6b37090ea11c76d8a14769ed9441058dd6f0b893","tid":586536,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"葉蔚琳早前向傳媒發出短訊，可見她收到了九巴的一封「終止僱用通知」。通知書上寫明在3月7日起終止僱用。其丈夫等三名車長同樣被解僱。在輿論壓力之下，資方暫緩解僱決定，葉蔚琳昨日已取回職員證。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yip_PAr8Y_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyip_PAr8Y_1200x0.png&h=3377c96d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"8d33cb710895366f454f42e587d7565b84fc4209","tid":586536,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:10:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}